D. Acquisition Strategy
The Common Missile Compartment (CMC) will be designed and developed to support the U.S. and UK in development of the COLUMBIA and DREADNOUGHT SSBN
programs enabling a common U.S.-UK CMC and maximizing the benefit of the ongoing U.S.-UK partnership in strategic deterrence. The COLUMBIA Class Program
RDT&E efforts will support the design, construction and operations & support portions of the program. RDT&E efforts will be performed by Navy laboratories, shipyards,
private industry, and University Affiliated Research Centers.




