Title: Other Aircraft Engine Component Improvement Program                                                                                   16.883      19.502         19.334
Description: CIP provides critical engineering support for approximately 8,000+ engines (e.g., TF33, TF34, T53, T56, T700,
T400, J85, F107), over 16,000 APU/SPS Propulsion Corporate Excellence (P-CORE) units, and critical developmental
engineering support for future engines (e.g., F404, F130). This also includes, engine issues associated with the C-130, T38,
