leverages technologies and expertise from across all of the Air Force Research Laboratories, integrating and
testing a variety of technologies.

FY 2025 Plans:
-Complete integration and test of COTS Rotax 916 turbo charged engine to enable ULTRA altitude and airspeed
for relevant geographically-constrained mission areas of interest.
