for scale up and formulation; conduct experiments and validate the in-house integrated materials engine and mesoscale model
framework to assess precursor cellulose strain processing, and scale up of nitrocellulose synthesis, strength models that
incorporate higher-fidelity physics such as crystal plasticity, crystallographic slip, and/or shear banding; determine final candidate

