Funds were erroneously transferred to PE 1203609SF and will be realigned back for proper execution towards:
- the continued development of optical communication terminal prototypes through Other Transaction Agreements and fund the
Optical Terminal Verification Testbed at Massachusetts Institute of Technology Lincoln Laboratory (MIT/LL).
- developing interface controls and integration plans in preparation for a space-based prototype demonstration. Mature networking
management of optical crosslink terminals in partnerships with other organizations.



