integration, at the system, ground, space, segment, and element levels. Integration supports across the enterprise Next Gen
OPIR, to include NGG SV1 final Space to Ground interface testing, launch base confidence testing, launch planning and NGG
SV2 mission payload and bus integration, as well as NGP SV1 & SV2 Bus and mission payload development, and Assembly,
