they become available. Coordinate with program offices for test, calibration, and tuning routines necessary for MEO and LEO
performance validation to ensure downstream warning and defense operations can ingest sensor data. The TAP Lab will
improve 3D tracks for observers in hybrid constellations into a Modeling & Simulation (M&S) tool to allow enterprise-level tracking
performance prediction against multiple scenarios based on data and analysis from multiple flight demo systems.

